
To build and install mod_authn_otp:

    1. Ensure you have the following software packages installed:

        apache2-devel
        openssl-devel
        apache2-dev (Ubuntu)
        build-essential (Ubuntu)

    2. Run `./configure'
    3. Run `make'
    4. Run `make install'

To configure apache to load the module:
    1. Write `LoadModule authn_otp_module /usr/lib/apache2/modules/mod_authn_otp.so` to `/etc/apache2/mods-available/authn_otp.load`
    2. Run `a2enmod authn_otp`

